{"tid":2193724,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國安多次查問 兩澳洲駐華記者急撤離中國 澳傳媒組織：中港對記者而言不安全","createTime":"2020-09-08T05:01:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T13:57:39.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"399d96bfa67ae0b6d5fc5414e0a80e2f90f103a1","tid":2193724,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:01:04.000Z","msg":"中澳兩國再出現外交風波。上周有澳洲駐華記者被國安人員上門問話，兩名記者的所屬傳媒機構已安排兩記者回澳。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲廣播公司駐北京記者 Bill Birtles 及《澳洲金融評論》 (Australian Financial Review) 駐上海記者 Mike Smith 上周多次被國安人員上門問話。上周初有駐澳外交官員提醒 Bill Birtles 盡早離開中國。澳洲外交部人員也有向澳洲廣播公司管理總監 David Anderson 提出相關建議。澳洲廣播公司隨即為 Bill Birtles 安排航機在上周四回國。<br />\n<br />\n不過在 Birtles 回國前的一日 (2/9) ，有 7 名中國公安在深夜前往 Birtles 在北京的居所，當時 Birtles 正與朋友和同事舉行告別派對⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://thestandnews.com/international/%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%A1%E6%9F%A5%E5%95%8F-%E5%85%A9%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E9%A7%90%E8%8F%AF%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%80%A5%E6%92%A4%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%BE%B3%E5%82%B3%E5%AA%92%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94-%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E5%B0%8D%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E8%80%8C%E8%A8%80%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%259F%25A5%25E5%2595%258F-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E9%25A7%2590%25E8%258F%25AF%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%2592%25A4%25E9%259B%25A2%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25AA%2592%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%2580%258C%25E8%25A8%2580%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%2F&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqFQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=3c8ccc07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%259F%25A5%25E5%2595%258F-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25